run(sql="
with cte as(
select a.orderDate, a.subOrderId, a.Channel, a.utmContent, b.pogId from `temp.orderAttri` a left join `last15Days(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
)
    select count(distinct a.subOrderId) as SD_Orders, 
            count(distinct case when lower(a.Channel) like 'fb%' then a.subOrderId end) as FB_Orders, 
            count(distinct case when lower(a.utmContent) like '%cpt%' then a.subOrderId end) as CPT_Orders 
    from cte a left join `temp.FB_Live_NewFeed` b 
    on a.pogId=b.dmPublisherInfoId
    where a.orderDate in ('2023-03-03','2023-03-04','2023-03-05','2023-03-06') 
    and lower(b.customLabel2) like '%sale%'
",1000)
